            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The overall aim of this tender is to secure a relationship with a preferred Contractor to provide Cleaning and Waste and related services as required for a venue’s busy programme of events.</P>
               <P>The objectives of the appointment of the preferred supplier includes:</P>
               <P>— to provide a professional, cost effective and quality service,</P>
               <P>— to provide a wide range of Cleaning and Waste services.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">5000000.00</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
